text.tspan: Tampa General Hospital integrated UpToDate into Epic and deployed
UpToDate Anywhere to provide access through the EMR and mobile devices.
The Veterans Health Administration adopted UpToDate Advanced
systemwide to help harmonize care and reduce clinical variation.
Vanderbilt University Medical Center implemented voice-enabled search for
UpToDate via Nuance Dragon Medical One.
Providence Clinical Network worked with Wolters Kluwer to use UpToDate
enterprise analytics dashboards to understand decision-support usage
Royal Devon adopted UpToDate Enterprise Edition, emphasizing AI-enhanced
search and analytics capabilities for clinicians and leaders.
NYU Langone Health made UpToDate Expert AI available to clinicians
through an institutional subscription as part of an early-access rollout.
